25/06/2007
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- Deputy Prime Minister Gordana Djurovic presented a draft national programme for EU integration Friday (June 22nd), covering 2008 to 2012. 
The draft outlines measures Montenegro must implement in order to meet obligations stemming from the Stabilisation and Association Agreement with the EU. 
The document will be open for public discussion before being adopted by the government. 
(Vijesti, Pobjeda - 23/06/07)
